notice: Notice to File Missing Parts of Application

missing_parts.description: The statutory basic filing fee is missing or insufficient.
The oath or declaration is missing or does not cover items omitted at the time of execution.
The oath or declaration does not identify the application to which it applies.
The signature of the following joint inventor(s) is missing from the oath or declaration.
A translation of the application and a fee of $30.00 under 37 CFR 1.17(k) is required.
A $50.00 processing fee is required for returned checks.
Your filing receipt was mailed in error because the check was returned without payment.

response_instructions.deadline: One month from the date of this letter or two months from the filing date, whichever is later.
response_instructions.extensions: Extensions of time may be obtained by filing a petition accompanied by the extension fee under the provisions of 37 CFR 1.135(a).
